## üìç Position Management

### Get All Positions
**Endpoint:** `GET /api/position/getAllPossition`

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "string",
  "message": "string",
  "data": [
    {
      "positionId": "number",
      "positionName": "string",
      "positionDescription": "string",
      "positionImage": "string"
    }
  ]
}
```

### Get Position by ID
**Endpoint:** `GET /api/position/getPositionById/{position_id}`

**Path Parameters:**
- `position_id` (integer)

### Create Position
**Endpoint:** `POST /api/position/createPosition`

**Content-Type:** `multipart/form-data`

**Form Data:**
- `positionName` (string)
- `positionDescription` (string)
- `positionImage` (binary)

### Update Position
**Endpoint:** `PUT /api/position/updatePositionById/{position_id}`

**Path Parameters:**
- `position_id` (integer)

**Content-Type:** `multipart/form-data`

**Form Data:**
- `positionName` (string)
- `positionDescription` (string)
- `positionImage` (binary)

### Delete Position
**Endpoint:** `DELETE /api/position/deletePositionById/{position_id}`

**Path Parameters:**
- `position_id` (integer)

